| Run command | Tests | Typical cover | Gate-safe at `fail_under=80`? |
|-------------|-------|---------------|-------------------------------|
| `pytest` | All | 96% | YES |
| `pytest -m "not integration"` | Unit | 92% | YES |
| `pytest -m integration` | Integ | ~78% | NO — partial-run trap |
| `pytest tests/foo.py::TestBar` | 5 | ~50% | NO — extreme partial run |

