| conftest location | `.parents[N]` |
|-------------------|---------------|
| `tests/conftest.py` | `parents[1]` |
| `tests/unit/conftest.py` | `parents[2]` |
| `tests/unit/analysis/conftest.py` | `parents[3]` |

